 Anthea’s objection was to your casually labeling Sandra Fluke as a “liberal cuckquean”.

Hi Bri,

I think The Notorious Anthea is a personal friend of Sandra Fluke. I have no desire to become ‘personal friends’ with this particular feminist; especially now that she has been de-friended by the Real Straight Men of Hermosa Beach, California; I like my men to know what they want (and need) in the bedroom – Not afraid of a spat, but quick enough to ‘take it like a man’.

I object to you casually making excuses for this nutjob Fluke. She is not clever enough; attractive enough or ‘witty enough’ – even in a nutty feminist sort of way – to come to her own conclusions in life. I grant that the SJW groupthink brainwashing she has taken part in probably warped her brain and her sense of self, but none of this can matter to her intellectually honest
